Dialogue: 4,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the fans are {\i1}very{\i0\fscx80} {\r} excited.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 4,0:04:03.12,0:04:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm looking forward to the show!"
Dialogue: 4,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll definitely be there!"
Dialogue: 4,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll follow Ryuuguu forever!"
Dialogue: 4,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:10.76,0:04:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all fan letters \Nfor Ryuuguu Komachi?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, from this month.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko-san has been \Nworking very hard, after all.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:18.62,0:04:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's steadily building–
Dialogue: 4,0:04:21.81,0:04:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:25.31,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this from Ritsuko's idol days?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see here.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Grandpa a look!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:31.44,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:34.38,0:04:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this is from that mini-concert...
Dialogue: 4,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you find it?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in this letter.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:42.80,0:04:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's a fan letter \Nfrom a "Petit Bellpepper-san."
Dialogue: 4,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't look anymore without asking!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Bellpepper?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:51.49,0:04:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of Ritsuko-san's diehard fans.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:54.28,0:04:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that Ritsuko-san \Nbecame a producer,
Dialogue: 4,0:04:57.39,0:05:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's following Ryuuguu Komachi now.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some devotion.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it nice that he's been \Nbehind you for so long?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the face of someone who \Nwants to make an idol comeback?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:13.03,0:05:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:15.21,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, we're going to put the \Nfinishing touches on your dance tomorrow!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'kay–
Dialogue: 4,0:05:21.10,0:05:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm feeling a little feverish.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to excuse myself first.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:27.56,0:05:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:28.91,0:05:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The concert is soon, \Nso please take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:33.28,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to take a lot \Nof vitamin C, and sleep!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest up as best you can.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko-san is completely \Nin Producer-mode.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:42.88,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you seen Azusa-san yet?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:54.07,0:05:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she just lost again?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:57.09,0:05:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:02.51,0:06:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azusa-san, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:08.35,0:06:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My fever just wouldn't go down,
Dialogue: 4,0:06:11.23,0:06:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}so I went to the hospital just in case.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They said it's the mumps.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mumps?!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then what about the show...?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:22.07,0:06:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It seems she has no choice but to rest until the fever and pain subside.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:26.83,0:06:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That normally takes four or five days.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:29.38,0:06:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should probably think that \Nshe can't come on stage.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to cancel the show?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fans are really looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you will just \Nhave to make do in her place.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:43.77,0:06:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, I'm sorry, \Nbut we have an emergency situation.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:47.48,0:06:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put on this show \Nwith Iori and Ami,
Dialogue: 4,0:06:49.92,0:06:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just the two of them.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:51.38,0:06:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you can all \Nhelp us follow through!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.56,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Kimi ga fureta kara nana iro Button
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.56,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Because you touched it, it's a rainbow button
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.02,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Subete wo koi de someta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.02,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}It dyes everything with the color of love
Dialogue: 4,0:07:00.76,0:07:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take out Azusa-san's solos for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:07.57,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Donna dekigoto mo koete yukeru tsuyosa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:07.57,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}And gives strength to overcome any event
Dialogue: 4,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and increase the overall \Nnumber of songs instead.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:05.63,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then I need to \Nrethink the order–
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.32,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Kimi ga boku ni kureta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.32,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}You gave it to me
Dialogue: 4,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But–!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are either of you hurt?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:16.65,0:07:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:17.79,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Azusa isn't here, \Nwe need to fill up the stage, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just trying to \Nemphasize our movements...
Dialogue: 4,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that with the \Ndance the way it is,
Dialogue: 4,0:07:28.08,0:07:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the empty space will stand out.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to alter it somehow.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:34.67,0:07:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with so little rehearsal time,
Dialogue: 4,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's just going to end up \Nfeeling unnatural.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:40.53,0:07:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:41.39,0:07:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we just get someone \Nto stand-in for Azusa?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:45.67,0:07:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way we could use the \Nchoreography the way we have it now.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:48.97,0:07:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! {KIMpossible!}
Dialogue: 4,0:07:49.81,0:07:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only four days \Nuntil the concert!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:51.83,0:07:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd need someone who could memorize the entire song and choreography.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:57.65,0:08:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can memorize the song \Nand choreography...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And has experience \Nstanding on stage.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:03.38,0:08:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone whose schedule fits...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:05.90,0:08:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And knows Ryuuguu Komachi inside and out.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:11.66,0:08:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! {ALT: I know! There is! etc}
Dialogue: 4,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd never work!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never never never!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's an emergency \Nsituation, so just give up!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fans are waiting, Ricchan!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M–Maybe, but–
Dialogue: 4,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to consider my \Nposition as a producer–
Dialogue: 4,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ask Nii-chan to fill in!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only person who can do it!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:31.14,0:08:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resign yourself!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W–Wait a second!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the request of \Na lifetime, Ricchan!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:39.02,0:08:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some time to think...!
