Dialogue: 4,0:08:49.26,0:08:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the number of songs we \Nhave and load up on talk time...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But doing just that \Nis really pushing it...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:55.58,0:08:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was Azusa-san's condition?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:58.09,0:09:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just called,
Dialogue: 4,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it sounds like she's \Njust taking it easy for now.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:03.47,0:09:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So things like this really happen.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it's a good \Nexperience for us, though.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Ritsuko...
Dialogue: 4,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Iori and the others,
Dialogue: 4,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but why don't you go \Nperform at the concert?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now even you're getting in on this?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that surprising?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've actually stood in \Nfront of fans as an idol,
Dialogue: 4,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so if you'd like, I'd take on \Nyour duties as Producer.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:27.07,0:09:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 4,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget this whole \Nthing ever happened.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. You all act like \Nit's not your problem.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Honey.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Thanks for coming in.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to \Nmemorize the song?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for the most part.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:41.54,0:09:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 4,0:09:42.53,0:09:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miki. Would you want to perform in the show as Azusa's stand-in?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:46.47,0:09:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we went with you, you could \Nmemorize the song and dance in a flash.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:49.38,0:09:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And didn't you say a while ago that you wanted to join Ryuuguu–
Dialogue: 4,0:09:53.72,0:09:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth am I saying?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:56.77,0:09:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How convenient would that be?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:58.63,0:10:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind doing it.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 4,0:10:03.38,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the way I see it, it would be best if you did it, Ritsuko...san.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:09.71,0:10:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I think Ritsuko...san would fit better in Ryuuguu Komachi than Miki would. {intentionally chose to include names rather than pronouns to show that miki is thinking more as a 'producer looking in' than as an individual, like ritsuko is. if it's too unnatural, can always change}
Dialogue: 4,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Good night.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:30.89,0:10:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I became a Producer, I decided to stop splitting up my resources.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:37.18,0:10:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Ryuuguu Komachi was \Nthe precious unit I first produced,
Dialogue: 4,0:10:42.33,0:10:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I didn't want to be irresponsible by having a side job like being an idol.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you think \Nabout it like a producer would?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make Ryuuguu \NKomachi's concert a success,
Dialogue: 4,0:10:54.97,0:10:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who is the most viable \Ncandidate at this point in time?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you already \Nhave your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:10.15,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Donna dekigoto mo koete yukeru tsuyosa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:10.15,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}And gives strength to overcome any event
Dialogue: 4,0:11:06.38,0:11:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stretch your fingertips!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're behind! You're behind!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we should go through \Nit with all three of us.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:15.59,0:11:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! I can't! I can't!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:18.21,0:11:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's only been thirty minutes!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W–Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:27.37,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Kimi ga fureta kara nana iro Button
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:27.37,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Because you touched it, it's a rainbow button
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.83,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Subete wo koi de someta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.83,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}It dyes everything with the color of love
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:35.42,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Donna dekigoto mo koete yukeru tsuyosa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:35.42,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}And gives strength to overcome any event
Dialogue: 4,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,I get it already! Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:39.14,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Kimi ga boku ni kureta
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:39.14,Button!,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}You gave it to me
Dialogue: 4,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I knew it. It's impossible.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:46.56,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In the first place, putting me on-stage in Azusa's place is just–
Dialogue: 4,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes? {these two lines COULD be lowered, but.. eh...}
Dialogue: 4,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Azusa-san!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:58.17,0:11:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really so sorry.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:59.68,0:12:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've caused you so much trouble...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N–No, don't say that...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, even though you might \Nget mad at me for saying this,
Dialogue: 4,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little happy.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:10.68,0:12:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you're going on \Nin my place, I mean.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:15.29,0:12:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's Iori-chan, Ami-chan, \Nthen me and Ritsuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:28.56,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSmudger LET\c&H495E57&\move(179,125,179,283,0,13270)}Diligence
Dialogue: 4,0:12:19.77,0:12:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The four of us make up \NRyuuguu Komachi, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azusa-san...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just fine here,
Dialogue: 4,0:12:26.86,0:12:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so get better soon, okay?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best,
Dialogue: 4,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please leave the show to us!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ricchan!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:39.79,0:12:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About your entrance at the concert...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:42.83,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be great to storm \Non-stage and then sing a solo?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:49.10,0:12:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a stand-in, \Nso I don't need a solo!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:52.88,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening! We need impact!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some song you want to sing?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there isn't!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:59.30,0:13:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet nobody even remembers \Nmy songs from when I was an idol!
