Dialogue: 4,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:05.82,0:13:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I \Ndon't have a single one...
Dialogue: 4,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I knew you had one.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:11.83,0:13:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's settled.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W–Wait!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:15.45,0:13:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just meant {\i1}if{\i0\fscx60} {\r} I was going to sing–
Dialogue: 4,0:13:21.67,0:13:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're starting dress \Nrehearsal for tomorrow's show!
