Dialogue: 4,0:14:17.40,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop the music!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:19.61,0:14:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:22.35,0:14:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U–Um, no.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:25.25,0:14:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S–Sorry. It's my first rehearsal in \Na while, so I got a little stage fright.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. What are you getting \Nstage fright during rehearsal for?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:32.97,0:14:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Sorry, Iori, Ami.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:35.92,0:14:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, please!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:38.55,0:14:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
