Dialogue: 4,0:15:01.19,0:15:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they come again today? \NThose fan letters for Ryuuguu.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:04.75,0:15:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:05.80,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been increasing \Nas the concert approaches.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it incredible?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:10.41,0:15:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it finally hit me today.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:13.08,0:15:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Iori and Ami have gone so far ahead of me when I was an idol.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:19.59,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I started thinking that I was going to stand on stage with girls like that,
Dialogue: 4,0:15:23.81,0:15:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:25.93,0:15:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko-san...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I said!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:31.54,0:15:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people we want \Nto invite to tomorrow's show!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:35.04,0:15:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do something \Nabout reserving their spots? {literally seats, but there are no 'seats' that i saw in the hall}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:37.32,0:15:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I could manage a few, but–
Dialogue: 4,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They hung up...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:47.24,0:15:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azusa-san!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:50.11,0:15:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I have a request \Nregarding tomorrow's concert...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at all of them!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:03.39,0:16:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all nice and pumped up.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. Break a leg.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give 'em a kick in the teeth!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:10.78,0:16:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:12.52,0:16:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W–What now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:17.19,0:16:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I–I totally want to go home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:22.72,0:16:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We're going on ahead.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:24.60,0:16:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get them all \Nwarmed up for your entrance!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:27.87,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S–Sure.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:31.87,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone–!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:33.61,0:16:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Ryuuguu Komachi's
Dialogue: 4,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Concert!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a bit of disappointing news.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:42.58,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, due to a bout of sudden illness, Azusa couldn't come tonight.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:47.18,0:16:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a message straight \Nfrom her, so listen up!
