Dialogue: 4,0:16:54.98,0:16:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Um, I'm sorry I \Nwasn't able to come tonight.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:59.91,0:17:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand up on stage, but I'm \Nsending all my love to you from here!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:05.22,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azusa-san...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she do this herself?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She called yesterday to \Nsay she'd recorded it,
Dialogue: 4,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wanted me to come pick it up.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally,
Dialogue: 4,0:17:15.46,0:17:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,standing in for me today, a very \Nspecial guest has decided to join us,
Dialogue: 4,0:17:22.48,0:17:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I hope you all enjoy the show!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:27.22,0:17:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh! Did those words \Nset off any alarm bells?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A special guest!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:31.74,0:17:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect for a "secret" show,
Dialogue: 4,0:17:34.40,0:17:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a very secret guest will arrive \Non stage right after this!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they get their hopes up, \Nthe pressure just builds and builds...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:42.32,0:17:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is a precious someone whose existence keeps Ryuuguu Komachi afloat!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though she's mega-scary \Nwhen she's mad,
Dialogue: 4,0:17:50.60,0:17:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's always really thinking about us. {ALT: ...about Ami and co.}
Dialogue: 4,0:17:54.13,0:18:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of her support that we're standing here right now!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our precious friend!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori... Ami...!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's introduce her!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuguu Komachi's producer,
Dialogue: 4,0:18:08.73,0:18:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and today, an idol from 765 Pro!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:12.12,0:18:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Akizuki Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Akizuki Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing w–with all my heart today!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you enjoy yourselves!
